          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Protect America's Schools Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill provides $1.5 billion in FY2018 supplemental appropriations to the Department of Justice Community Oriented Policing Services (COPS) program for school resource officers. </p> <p>The bill also rescinds $1.5 billion of the unobligated appropriations available to the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration for Operations, Research, and Facilities. </p>]]></text>
